parsed.explanation: 1. Corrected invalid XML nesting by inserting a closing </BIBL> tag after the Mohemii entry, which was incorrectly wrapping the subsequent Titus Livius entry. 2. Separated the authors ('Janii & Tremellii') from the title in the first entry to conform to the standard <AUTHOR>/<TITLE> structure used elsewhere. 3. Normalized four instances of corrupted Unicode sequences (e.g., 'B\u221a\u00bacher' to 'Bücher', '4t\u221a\u2264' to '4tô') to their correct characters.
